description: After a highly satisfying first romp, Ryan Stone and Jay Dymel are yearning for a second round with Markus Kage. Not only was the first job an easy one. for the hunky boxer, but he also pocketed a handsome sum. He begins to contemplate whether professional boxing is really the best choice for him, while quickly agreeing to another equally lucrative assignment.
title: FRIENDLY FIRE: PART 2 RAW
